@startuml
[*] --> StartCampaign: Manager and staff assigned
StartCampaign --> ActivateCampaign: Everything approved and contract signed
ActivateCampaign --> PrepareAdverts: Campaign preparation
PrepareAdverts --> ApproveAndScheduleAdverts: Advert approval and scheduling
ApproveAndScheduleAdverts --> RunAdverts: Advert running
RunAdverts --> ExtendOrAdjustCampaign: Extension or adjustment of campaign while running
ExtendOrAdjustCampaign --> CompleteCampaign: Final statement after all adverts finished
CompleteCampaign --> HandlePayment: Payment handling after campaign completion
HandlePayment --> RefundIfLessThanRequired : Generate refund if amount paid is less than required
RefundIfLessThanRequired --> WaitForCorrectBalance: Wait for correct balance to be settled if amount paid exceeds required amount
WaitForCorrectBalance --> MarkAsPaid: Mark campaign as paid once full amount properly paid
MarkAsPaid --> ArchiveCampaign: Campaign archiving and staff/manager release

@enduml
